# TaskSyncPro

![.NET](https://img.shields.io/badge/.NET-10.0-blue) ![C#](https://img.shields.io/badge/C%23-12-green) ![EF%20Core](https://img.shields.io/badge/EF%20Core-9.0.11-orange)

TaskSyncPro is a layered ASP.NET Core 10.0 Web API for enterprise task, team, employee, role, billing, and activity logging management. It enforces validated workflows, provides auditable task activity, and separates presentation, business logic, and data access concerns.

---

